body:
@cdjkim - Might be a copy-paste error but it doesn't look like you're actually running the init op. Rather than:

```
sess = tf.Session()
init = tf.initialize_all_variables().run
print sess.run(r)
```

try:

```
sess = tf.Session()
sess.run(tf.initialize_all_variables())
print sess.run(r)
```
